div.h1: Multi-Process VGA Demo: Memory-Mapped I/O Sharing
div.p: 3 concurrent kernel processes sharing one identity-mapped VGA buffer at 0xB8000

Buffer layout: 80 cols x 25 rows = 2000 cells x 2 bytes
Process A Region rows 0-7 offset 0x0000-0x0A00 1280 bytes
